James Haven https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Haven 0 James Haven (born James Haven Voight, May 11, 1973) is an American actor and producer. He is the son of actors Jon Voight and Marcheline Bertrand, and the older brother of actress Angelina Jolie.
